**Horsemen** | Ability Set
Passive: Emit `ApocalypseCheck`
On `ApocalypseCheck` Emitted: Role Change @Self to `Apocalyptic Horseman` [Condition: not (@(Align:!Horsemen,Class:!Unaligned,Attr:!Doomed) exists), Condition: not (@(Align:Horsemen,Group:!Horsemen) exists), Condition: @Self->Role is not `Apocalyptic Horseman`]
